{{#paper-card as |card|}}
{{#card.title as |title|}}
    {{#title.text as |text|}}
      {{#text.headline}}Herzlich Willkommen!{{/text.headline}}
      {{#text.subhead}}{{/text.subhead}}
    {{/title.text}}
  {{/card.title}}
  {{#card.content}}
  {{currentUser.user.salutation}} {{currentUser.user.surname}},
  <br/>
  Hier können Sie aktuelle und vergangene Anmerkungen der Studierenden anschauen.
  Die Kommentare werden von uns, der Fachschaft, sortiert und mögliche Beleidigungen gelöscht.
  Danke für Ihre Bemühungen!
  <br/>
  Ihre Fachschaft MathPhys
  {{/card.content}}
{{/paper-card}}

  {{#each model as |complaint|}}
    {{#paper-card as |card|}}
    {{#card.title as |title|}}
        {{#title.text as |text|}}
          {{#text.headline}}{{complaint.course.name}}{{/text.headline}}
          {{#text.subhead}}{{moment-format complaint.createdAt locale='de'}}{{/text.subhead}}
        {{/title.text}}
      {{/card.title}}
      {{#card.content}}
      {{simple-mde-preview complaint.message}}
      {{/card.content}}
      {{#card.actions}}
      {{#paper-button onClick=(action "markasread" complaint)}}Als gelesen markieren{{/paper-button}}
      {{/card.actions}}
    {{/paper-card}}
    {{else}}
    {{#paper-card as |card|}}
      {{#card.content}}
        Aktuell sind keine neuen Kummer verfügbar.
      {{/card.content}}
    {{/paper-card}}
  {{/each}}
  {{outlet}}
